{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"What I'm going to try to do is explain to you"},{"time":3000,"text":"quickly how to predict,"},{"time":5000,"text":"and illustrate it with some predictions"},{"time":7000,"text":"about what Iran is going to do in the next couple of years."}]},{"cues":[{"time":12000,"text":"In order to predict effectively,"},{"time":15000,"text":"we need to use science."},{"time":18000,"text":"And the reason that we need to use science"},{"time":21000,"text":"is because then we can reproduce what we're doing;"},{"time":23000,"text":"it's not just wisdom or guesswork."},{"time":26000,"text":"And if we can predict,"},{"time":29000,"text":"then we can engineer the future."},{"time":31000,"text":"So if you are concerned to influence energy policy,"},{"time":35000,"text":"or you are concerned to influence national security policy,"},{"time":40000,"text":"or health policy, or education,"},{"time":43000,"text":"science -- and a particular branch of science -- is a way to do it,"},{"time":47000,"text":"not the way we've been doing it,"},{"time":49000,"text":"which is seat-of-the-pants wisdom."}]},{"cues":[{"time":51000,"text":"Now before I get into how to do it"},{"time":53000,"text":"let me give you a little truth in advertising,"},{"time":56000,"text":"because I'm not engaged in the business of magic."},{"time":59000,"text":"There are lots of thing that the approach I take can predict,"},{"time":63000,"text":"and there are some that it can't."},{"time":65000,"text":"It can predict complex negotiations"},{"time":68000,"text":"or situations involving coercion --"},{"time":71000,"text":"that is in essence everything that has to do with politics,"},{"time":75000,"text":"much of what has to do with business,"},{"time":77000,"text":"but sorry, if you're looking to speculate in the stock market,"},{"time":83000,"text":"I don't predict stock markets -- OK,"},{"time":85000,"text":"it's not going up any time really soon."},{"time":88000,"text":"But I'm not engaged in doing that."},{"time":91000,"text":"I'm not engaged in predicting random number generators."},{"time":94000,"text":"I actually get phone calls from people"},{"time":96000,"text":"who want to know what lottery numbers are going to win."},{"time":99000,"text":"I don't have a clue."}]},{"cues":[{"time":102000,"text":"I engage in the use of game theory, game theory is a branch of mathematics"},{"time":106000,"text":"and that means, sorry, that even in the study of politics,"},{"time":110000,"text":"math has come into the picture."},{"time":113000,"text":"We can no longer pretend that we just speculate about politics,"},{"time":117000,"text":"we need to look at this in a rigorous way."},{"time":120000,"text":"Now, what is game theory about?"},{"time":123000,"text":"It assumes that people are looking out for what's good for them."},{"time":128000,"text":"That doesn't seem terribly shocking --"},{"time":130000,"text":"although it's controversial for a lot of people --"},{"time":132000,"text":"that we are self-interested."},{"time":136000,"text":"In order to look out for what's best for them"},{"time":138000,"text":"or what they think is best for them,"},{"time":140000,"text":"people have values -- they identify what they want, and what they don't want."},{"time":144000,"text":"And they have beliefs about what other people want,"},{"time":147000,"text":"and what other people don't want, how much power other people have,"},{"time":150000,"text":"how much those people could get in the way of whatever it is that you want."},{"time":154000,"text":"And they face limitations, constraints,"},{"time":158000,"text":"they may be weak, they may be located in the wrong part of the world,"},{"time":161000,"text":"they may be Einstein, stuck away farming"},{"time":164000,"text":"someplace in a rural village in India not being noticed,"},{"time":168000,"text":"as was the case for Ramanujan for a long time,"},{"time":171000,"text":"a great mathematician but nobody noticed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":174000,"text":"Now who is rational?"},{"time":176000,"text":"A lot of people are worried about what is rationality about?"},{"time":179000,"text":"You know, what if people are rational?"},{"time":181000,"text":"Mother Theresa, she was rational."},{"time":184000,"text":"Terrorists, they're rational."},{"time":188000,"text":"Pretty much everybody is rational."},{"time":191000,"text":"I think there are only two exceptions that I'm aware of --"},{"time":194000,"text":"two-year-olds, they are not rational,"},{"time":196000,"text":"they have very fickle preferences,"},{"time":199000,"text":"they switch what they think all the time,"},{"time":201000,"text":"and schizophrenics are probably not rational,"},{"time":204000,"text":"but pretty much everybody else is rational."},{"time":206000,"text":"That is, they are just trying to do"},{"time":208000,"text":"what they think is in their own best interest."}]},{"cues":[{"time":213000,"text":"Now in order to work out what people are going to do"},{"time":215000,"text":"to pursue their interests,"},{"time":217000,"text":"we have to think about who has influence in the world."},{"time":219000,"text":"If you're trying to influence corporations to change their behavior,"},{"time":224000,"text":"with regard to producing pollutants,"},{"time":227000,"text":"one approach, the common approach,"},{"time":229000,"text":"is to exhort them to be better,"},{"time":231000,"text":"to explain to them what damage they're doing to the planet."},{"time":234000,"text":"And many of you may have noticed that doesn't have"},{"time":236000,"text":"as big an effect, as perhaps you would like it to have."},{"time":240000,"text":"But if you show them that it's in their interest,"},{"time":243000,"text":"then they're responsive."}]},{"cues":[{"time":245000,"text":"So, we have to work out who influences problems."},{"time":248000,"text":"If we're looking at Iran, the president of the United States"},{"time":250000,"text":"we would like to think, may have some influence --"},{"time":253000,"text":"certainly the president in Iran has some influence --"},{"time":257000,"text":"but we make a mistake if we just pay attention"},{"time":260000,"text":"to the person at the top of the power ladder"},{"time":263000,"text":"because that person doesn't know much about Iran,"},{"time":266000,"text":"or about energy policy,"},{"time":268000,"text":"or about health care,"},{"time":270000,"text":"or about any particular policy."},{"time":272000,"text":"That person surrounds himself or herself with advisers."},{"time":277000,"text":"If we're talking about national security problems,"},{"time":279000,"text":"maybe it's the Secretary of State,"},{"time":281000,"text":"maybe it's the Secretary of Defense,"},{"time":283000,"text":"the Director of National Intelligence,"},{"time":285000,"text":"maybe the ambassador to the United Nations, or somebody else"},{"time":287000,"text":"who they think is going to know more about the particular problem."},{"time":291000,"text":"But let's face it, the Secretary of State doesn't know much about Iran."},{"time":294000,"text":"The secretary of defense doesn't know much about Iran."},{"time":297000,"text":"Each of those people in turn"},{"time":300000,"text":"has advisers who advise them,"},{"time":302000,"text":"so they can advise the president."},{"time":305000,"text":"There are lots of people shaping decisions"},{"time":308000,"text":"and so if we want to predict correctly"},{"time":310000,"text":"we have to pay attention to everybody"},{"time":313000,"text":"who is trying to shape the outcome,"},{"time":315000,"text":"not just the people at the pinnacle"},{"time":318000,"text":"of the decision-making pyramid."}]},{"cues":[{"time":322000,"text":"Unfortunately, a lot of times we don't do that."},{"time":324000,"text":"There's a good reason that we don't do that,"},{"time":326000,"text":"and there's a good reason that using game theory and computers,"},{"time":329000,"text":"we can overcome the limitation"},{"time":332000,"text":"of just looking at a few people."},{"time":334000,"text":"Imagine a problem with just five decision-makers."},{"time":338000,"text":"Imagine for example"},{"time":340000,"text":"that Sally over here,"},{"time":342000,"text":"wants to know what Harry, and Jane,"},{"time":345000,"text":"and George and Frank are thinking,"},{"time":348000,"text":"and sends messages to those people."},{"time":350000,"text":"Sally's giving her opinion to them,"},{"time":352000,"text":"and they're giving their opinion to Sally."},{"time":355000,"text":"But Sally also wants to know"},{"time":357000,"text":"what Harry is saying to these three,"},{"time":360000,"text":"and what they're saying to Harry."},{"time":362000,"text":"And Harry wants to know"},{"time":364000,"text":"what each of those people are saying to each other, and so on,"},{"time":367000,"text":"and Sally would like to know what Harry thinks those people are saying."},{"time":370000,"text":"That's a complicated problem; that's a lot to know."},{"time":373000,"text":"With five decision-makers"},{"time":376000,"text":"there are a lot of linkages --"},{"time":378000,"text":"120, as a matter of fact,"},{"time":380000,"text":"if you remember your factorials."},{"time":382000,"text":"Five factorial is 120."},{"time":384000,"text":"Now you may be surprised to know"},{"time":386000,"text":"that smart people can keep 120 things straight"},{"time":389000,"text":"in their head."},{"time":391000,"text":"Suppose we double the number of influencers"},{"time":393000,"text":"from five to 10."},{"time":395000,"text":"Does that mean we've doubled the number of pieces of information"},{"time":399000,"text":"we need to know, from 120 to 240?"},{"time":401000,"text":"No. How about 10 times?"},{"time":403000,"text":"To 1,200? No."},{"time":406000,"text":"We've increased it to 3.6 million."},{"time":409000,"text":"Nobody can keep that straight in their head."},{"time":411000,"text":"But computers,"},{"time":414000,"text":"they can. They don't need coffee breaks,"},{"time":417000,"text":"they don't need vacations,"},{"time":420000,"text":"they don't need to go to sleep at night,"},{"time":422000,"text":"they don't ask for raises either."},{"time":425000,"text":"They can keep this information straight"},{"time":427000,"text":"and that means that we can process the information."}]},{"cues":[{"time":430000,"text":"So I'm going to talk to you about how to process it,"},{"time":432000,"text":"and I'm going to give you some examples out of Iran,"},{"time":435000,"text":"and you're going to be wondering,"},{"time":437000,"text":"\"Why should we listen to this guy?"},{"time":439000,"text":"Why should we believe what he's saying?\""},{"time":442000,"text":"So I'm going to show you a factoid."},{"time":446000,"text":"This is an assessment by the Central Intelligence Agency"},{"time":449000,"text":"of the percentage of time"},{"time":451000,"text":"that the model I'm talking about"},{"time":453000,"text":"is right in predicting things whose outcome is not yet known,"},{"time":456000,"text":"when the experts who provided the data inputs"},{"time":460000,"text":"got it wrong."},{"time":462000,"text":"That's not my claim, that's a CIA claim -- you can read it,"},{"time":465000,"text":"it was declassified a while ago. You can read it in a volume edited by"},{"time":468000,"text":"H. Bradford Westerfield, Yale University Press."}]},{"cues":[{"time":471000,"text":"So, what do we need to know"},{"time":473000,"text":"in order to predict?"},{"time":475000,"text":"You may be surprised to find out we don't need to know very much."},{"time":478000,"text":"We do need to know who has a stake"},{"time":481000,"text":"in trying to shape the outcome of a decision."},{"time":486000,"text":"We need to know what they say they want,"},{"time":489000,"text":"not what they want in their heart of hearts,"},{"time":492000,"text":"not what they think they can get,"},{"time":494000,"text":"but what they say they want, because that is a strategically chosen position,"},{"time":497000,"text":"and we can work backwards from that"},{"time":499000,"text":"to draw inferences about important features of their decision-making."},{"time":503000,"text":"We need to know how focused they are"},{"time":505000,"text":"on the problem at hand."},{"time":507000,"text":"That is, how willing are they to drop what they're doing when the issue comes up,"},{"time":510000,"text":"and attend to it instead of something else that's on their plate --"},{"time":514000,"text":"how big a deal is it to them?"},{"time":516000,"text":"And how much clout could they bring to bear"},{"time":519000,"text":"if they chose to engage on the issue?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":524000,"text":"If we know those things"},{"time":526000,"text":"we can predict their behavior by assuming that everybody"},{"time":529000,"text":"cares about two things on any decision."},{"time":534000,"text":"They care about the outcome. They'd like an outcome as close to"},{"time":536000,"text":"what they are interested in as possible."},{"time":539000,"text":"They're careerists, they also care about getting credit --"},{"time":542000,"text":"there's ego involvement,"},{"time":544000,"text":"they want to be seen as important in shaping the outcome,"},{"time":548000,"text":"or as important, if it's their druthers, to block an outcome."},{"time":553000,"text":"And so we have to figure out how they balance those two things."},{"time":556000,"text":"Different people trade off"},{"time":558000,"text":"between standing by their outcome,"},{"time":561000,"text":"faithfully holding to it, going down in a blaze of glory,"},{"time":564000,"text":"or giving it up, putting their finger in the wind,"},{"time":567000,"text":"and doing whatever they think is going to be a winning position."},{"time":570000,"text":"Most people fall in between, and if we can work out where they fall"},{"time":573000,"text":"we can work out how to negotiate with them"},{"time":575000,"text":"to change their behavior."}]},{"cues":[{"time":577000,"text":"So with just that little bit of input"},{"time":580000,"text":"we can work out what the choices are that people have,"},{"time":583000,"text":"what the chances are that they're willing to take,"},{"time":586000,"text":"what they're after, what they value, what they want,"},{"time":589000,"text":"and what they believe about other people."},{"time":592000,"text":"You might notice what we don't need to know:"},{"time":596000,"text":"there's no history in here."},{"time":598000,"text":"How they got to where they are"},{"time":600000,"text":"may be important in shaping the input information,"},{"time":602000,"text":"but once we know where they are"},{"time":604000,"text":"we're worried about where they're going to be headed in the future."},{"time":607000,"text":"How they got there turns out not to be terribly critical in predicting."},{"time":611000,"text":"I remind you of that 90 percent accuracy rate."}]},{"cues":[{"time":615000,"text":"So where are we going to get this information?"},{"time":617000,"text":"We can get this information"},{"time":620000,"text":"from the Internet, from The Economist,"},{"time":623000,"text":"The Financial Times, The New York Times,"},{"time":626000,"text":"U.S. News and World Report, lots of sources like that,"},{"time":629000,"text":"or we can get it from asking experts"},{"time":631000,"text":"who spend their lives studying places and problems,"},{"time":634000,"text":"because those experts know this information."},{"time":637000,"text":"If they don't know, who are the people trying to influence the decision,"},{"time":640000,"text":"how much clout do they have,"},{"time":642000,"text":"how much they care about this issue, and what do they say they want,"},{"time":645000,"text":"are they experts? That's what it means to be an expert,"},{"time":648000,"text":"that's the basic stuff an expert needs to know."}]},{"cues":[{"time":652000,"text":"Alright, lets turn to Iran."},{"time":654000,"text":"Let me make three important predictions --"},{"time":657000,"text":"you can check this out, time will tell."},{"time":660000,"text":"What is Iran going to do about its nuclear weapons program?"},{"time":668000,"text":"How secure is the theocratic regime in Iran?"},{"time":671000,"text":"What's its future?"},{"time":673000,"text":"And everybody's best friend,"},{"time":676000,"text":"Ahmadinejad. How are things going for him?"},{"time":679000,"text":"How are things going to be working out for him in the next year or two?"},{"time":685000,"text":"You take a look at this, this is not based on statistics."},{"time":688000,"text":"I want to be very clear here. I'm not projecting some past data into the future."},{"time":693000,"text":"I've taken inputs on positions and so forth,"},{"time":696000,"text":"run it through a computer model"},{"time":698000,"text":"that had simulated the dynamics of interaction,"},{"time":701000,"text":"and these are the simulated dynamics,"},{"time":703000,"text":"the predictions about the path of policy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":706000,"text":"So you can see here on the vertical axis,"},{"time":709000,"text":"I haven't shown it all the way down to zero,"},{"time":711000,"text":"there are lots of other options, but here I'm just showing you the prediction,"},{"time":714000,"text":"so I've narrowed the scale."},{"time":716000,"text":"Up at the top of the axis, \"Build the Bomb.\""},{"time":719000,"text":"At 130, we start somewhere above 130,"},{"time":723000,"text":"between building a bomb, and making enough weapons-grade fuel"},{"time":726000,"text":"so that you could build a bomb."},{"time":728000,"text":"That's where, according to my analyses,"},{"time":731000,"text":"the Iranians were at the beginning of this year."},{"time":734000,"text":"And then the model makes predictions down the road."},{"time":737000,"text":"At 115 they would only produce enough weapons grade fuel"},{"time":741000,"text":"to show that they know how, but they wouldn't build a weapon:"},{"time":743000,"text":"they would build a research quantity."},{"time":745000,"text":"It would achieve some national pride,"},{"time":747000,"text":"but not go ahead and build a weapon."},{"time":750000,"text":"And down at 100 they would build civilian nuclear energy,"},{"time":752000,"text":"which is what they say is their objective."}]},{"cues":[{"time":756000,"text":"The yellow line shows us the most likely path."},{"time":759000,"text":"The yellow line includes an analysis"},{"time":760000,"text":"of 87 decision makers in Iran,"},{"time":763000,"text":"and a vast number of outside influencers"},{"time":766000,"text":"trying to pressure Iran into changing its behavior,"},{"time":769000,"text":"various players in the United States, and Egypt,"},{"time":772000,"text":"and Saudi Arabia, and Russia, European Union,"},{"time":774000,"text":"Japan, so on and so forth."},{"time":776000,"text":"The white line reproduces the analysis"},{"time":780000,"text":"if the international environment"},{"time":782000,"text":"just left Iran to make its own internal decisions,"},{"time":785000,"text":"under its own domestic political pressures."},{"time":787000,"text":"That's not going to be happening,"},{"time":789000,"text":"but you can see that the line comes down faster"},{"time":793000,"text":"if they're not put under international pressure,"},{"time":796000,"text":"if they're allowed to pursue their own devices."}]},{"cues":[{"time":798000,"text":"But in any event, by the end of this year,"},{"time":801000,"text":"beginning of next year, we get to a stable equilibrium outcome."},{"time":804000,"text":"And that equilibrium is not what the United States would like,"},{"time":808000,"text":"but it's probably an equilibrium that the United States can live with,"},{"time":811000,"text":"and that a lot of others can live with."},{"time":813000,"text":"And that is that Iran will achieve that nationalist pride"},{"time":817000,"text":"by making enough weapons-grade fuel, through research,"},{"time":821000,"text":"so that they could show that they know how to make weapons-grade fuel,"},{"time":825000,"text":"but not enough to actually build a bomb."},{"time":830000,"text":"How is this happening?"},{"time":832000,"text":"Over here you can see this is the distribution"},{"time":836000,"text":"of power in favor of civilian nuclear energy today,"},{"time":841000,"text":"this is what that power block is predicted to be like"},{"time":844000,"text":"by the late parts of 2010, early parts of 2011."},{"time":850000,"text":"Just about nobody supports research on weapons-grade fuel today,"},{"time":854000,"text":"but by 2011 that gets to be a big block,"},{"time":857000,"text":"and you put these two together, that's the controlling influence in Iran."}]},{"cues":[{"time":861000,"text":"Out here today, there are a bunch of people --"},{"time":864000,"text":"Ahmadinejad for example --"},{"time":866000,"text":"who would like not only to build a bomb,"},{"time":868000,"text":"but test a bomb."},{"time":870000,"text":"That power disappears completely;"},{"time":872000,"text":"nobody supports that by 2011."},{"time":875000,"text":"These guys are all shrinking,"},{"time":877000,"text":"the power is all drifting out here,"},{"time":880000,"text":"so the outcome is going to be the weapons-grade fuel."}]},{"cues":[{"time":883000,"text":"Who are the winners and who are the losers in Iran?"},{"time":886000,"text":"Take a look at these guys, they're growing in power,"},{"time":889000,"text":"and by the way, this was done a while ago"},{"time":892000,"text":"before the current economic crisis,"},{"time":894000,"text":"and that's probably going to get steeper."},{"time":896000,"text":"These folks are the moneyed interests in Iran,"},{"time":898000,"text":"the bankers, the oil people, the bazaaries."},{"time":902000,"text":"They are growing in political clout,"},{"time":905000,"text":"as the mullahs are isolating themselves --"},{"time":908000,"text":"with the exception of one group of mullahs,"},{"time":910000,"text":"who are not well known to Americans."},{"time":912000,"text":"That's this line here, growing in power,"},{"time":914000,"text":"these are what the Iranians call the quietists."},{"time":918000,"text":"These are the Ayatollahs, mostly based in Qom,"},{"time":921000,"text":"who have great clout in the religious community,"},{"time":925000,"text":"have been quiet on politics and are going to be getting louder,"},{"time":928000,"text":"because they see Iran going in an unhealthy direction,"},{"time":930000,"text":"a direction contrary"},{"time":932000,"text":"to what Khomeini had in mind."},{"time":936000,"text":"Here is Mr. Ahmadinejad."},{"time":938000,"text":"Two things to notice: he's getting weaker,"},{"time":941000,"text":"and while he gets a lot of attention in the United States,"},{"time":943000,"text":"he is not a major player in Iran."},{"time":945000,"text":"He is on the way down."}]},{"cues":[{"time":947000,"text":"OK, so I'd like you to take a little away from this."},{"time":951000,"text":"Everything is not predictable: the stock market"},{"time":953000,"text":"is, at least for me, not predictable,"},{"time":956000,"text":"but most complicated negotiations are predictable."},{"time":961000,"text":"Again, whether we're talking health policy, education,"},{"time":965000,"text":"environment, energy,"},{"time":968000,"text":"litigation, mergers,"},{"time":970000,"text":"all of these are complicated problems"},{"time":972000,"text":"that are predictable,"},{"time":974000,"text":"that this sort of technology can be applied to."},{"time":978000,"text":"And the reason that being able to predict those things is important,"},{"time":983000,"text":"is not just because you might run a hedge fund and make money off of it,"},{"time":986000,"text":"but because if you can predict what people will do,"},{"time":989000,"text":"you can engineer what they will do."},{"time":992000,"text":"And if you engineer what they do you can change the world,"},{"time":994000,"text":"you can get a better result."},{"time":996000,"text":"I would like to leave you with one thought, which is"},{"time":999000,"text":"for me, the dominant theme of this gathering,"},{"time":1004000,"text":"and is the dominant theme of this way of thinking about the world."},{"time":1007000,"text":"When people say to you,"},{"time":1010000,"text":"\"That's impossible,\""},{"time":1012000,"text":"you say back to them,"},{"time":1014000,"text":"\"When you say 'That's impossible,'"},{"time":1016000,"text":"you're confused with,"},{"time":1018000,"text":"'I don't know how to do it.'\""},{"time":1021000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1023000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1027000,"text":"Chris Anderson: One question for you."},{"time":1029000,"text":"That was fascinating."},{"time":1032000,"text":"I love that you put it out there."},{"time":1035000,"text":"I got very nervous halfway through the talk though,"},{"time":1037000,"text":"just panicking whether you'd included in your model, the possibility that"},{"time":1040000,"text":"putting this prediction out there might change the result."},{"time":1044000,"text":"We've got 800 people in Tehran who watch TEDTalks."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1047000,"text":"Bruce Bueno de Mesquita: I've thought about that,"},{"time":1049000,"text":"and since I've done a lot of work for the intelligence community,"},{"time":1053000,"text":"they've also pondered that."},{"time":1055000,"text":"It would be a good thing if"},{"time":1058000,"text":"people paid more attention, took seriously,"},{"time":1061000,"text":"and engaged in the same sorts of calculations,"},{"time":1063000,"text":"because it would change things. But it would change things in two beneficial ways."},{"time":1067000,"text":"It would hasten how quickly people arrive at an agreement,"},{"time":1073000,"text":"and so it would save everybody a lot of grief and time."},{"time":1076000,"text":"And, it would arrive at an agreement that everybody was happy with,"},{"time":1080000,"text":"without having to manipulate them so much --"},{"time":1083000,"text":"which is basically what I do, I manipulate them."},{"time":1086000,"text":"So it would be a good thing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1088000,"text":"CA: So you're kind of trying to say, \"People of Iran, this is your destiny, lets go there.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":1092000,"text":"BBM: Well, people of Iran, this is what many of you are going to evolve to want,"},{"time":1098000,"text":"and we could get there a lot sooner,"},{"time":1100000,"text":"and you would suffer a lot less trouble from economic sanctions,"},{"time":1103000,"text":"and we would suffer a lot less fear of the use of military force on our end,"},{"time":1109000,"text":"and the world would be a better place."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1111000,"text":"CA: Here's hoping they hear it that way. Thank you very much Bruce."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1114000,"text":"BBM: Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1116000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}